first we need to install gedit editor at our linux mint - virtual machine
for that we need to run the following codes

- Install command: sudo apt-get install gedit 
- Usage command: gedit yourFileName 

gedit HelloWorld
(on the file HelloWorld):
#!/bin/bash
echo “Hello world”
(back to terminal)
# give autorizathion to the file
chmod 755 HelloWorld
# run the file
./HelloWorld
